             was indicted for the <rs id="t17750218-59-off299" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17750218-59-off299" type="offenceCategory" value="kill"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17750218-59-off299" type="offenceSubcategory" value="murder"></interp>
